The memorial service of vocalist, Nichume Siwundla is currently underway at the Assemblies of God church in Sandton, Johannesburg. The 27-year-old singer committed suicide at a friend’s house in Joburg last week. READ: VOCALIST NICHUME COMMITS SUICIDE! Today Nichume's life is being celebrated by all who loved her and her work. DJ Tira and NaakMusiq were among those who spoke at the late singers memorial service. Songstress Shekinah and media personality Moshe Ndiki we also among the attendees who came to celebrate Nichume's life. Nichume's Funeral will be held in East London, Beacon Bay on Saturday, June 15. Follow live tweets here:  